{"tid":1464801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日香港算有運 運動差啲玩完 一定要大力宣傳公安示威者打人","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:31:57.000Z","uid":105995,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cbcc907f2c3f453a88888b6e8e0346d4082e3f9f","tid":1464801,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:29:27.000Z","msg":"大家覺唔覺公安單嘢其實好兇險?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463835\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463835</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n多謝上面呢位巴打提醒 愈諗愈覺得今日兇險<br />\n<br />\n香港今次算有運<br />\n<br />\n好彩警隊臥底 同公安單野及時踢爆 冇俾佢地進一步行動<br />\n<br />\n唔係我地已經唔知點拆 運動隨時玩完<br />\n<br />\n所以我地一定要大力宣傳公安單野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">等大家有個底 等大眾心裹面有中共嫁喎嘅concept<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n中共之後出大量賤招嫁禍示威者 都有得拆下"},{"pid":"a2d3ee04ef7a2d6ee969f23dc54ed2647c8d9a69","tid":1464801,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:30:06.000Z","msg":"【入黎】我正式宣佈，今日輸撚咗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464718</a>"},{"pid":"40a08f04e3a0c418c5e4a7be21f35910bcba6d1d","tid":1464801,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf1fb4aac45b9d808d838625316f115279a25c8","tid":1464801,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"扮示威者 自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}